DESCRIPTION:Since 2010\, The North Carolina Digital Heritage Center (NCDHC)
  has worked with North Carolina’s cultural heritage organizations to scan\,
  describe\, and publish historical materials online. Hear from employees of
  the NCDHC about the work of the Center\, interesting materials\, and their
  favorite partnerships.\n\n \n\nThe Library Discovery Hour Series aims to p
 rovide an inside look into today’s University Library at Carolina. Join us 
 to discover new perspectives and delve into fascinating topics that showcas
 e the impact of the Library on every Tar Heel.
