 e uses soft textures and also encourages touch in her artworks to soothe dr
 eads and worries about the world. \nParticipation is free and at your pace\
 , but RSVPs are encouraged to guarantee a stuffie is available for your use
 . Please register below for your free individual ticket. Otherwise\, they w
 ill be available first come\, first served.
