BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:The current economic climate brings both challenges and opportu
 nities from a financial perspective. You may wonder during these challengin
 g times: “What should I be most careful about” and “What should my family a
 nd I work towards?” The 10 financial tips discussed in this workshop will g
 et you on the road to financial well-being during challenging times.\n\n \n
 \nWorkshop Objectives\nAt the end of this workshop\, you will be able to:\n
 Identify the most pressing/immediate financial steps to take in your life\n
 • Describe why an emergency fund is an absolute necessity\n• Identify how t
 o categorize types of expenses\n• Describe your current financial position 
 by putting it on paper\nDescribe steps to help you through economic trouble
 s\n• Describe how to begin paying down debts\n• Identify ways to improve yo
 ur credit score\nDescribe ways to build long-term plans for your financial 
 health\n• Describe how to evaluate your insurance coverage\n• Identify how 
 to build or refine your retirement plans\n\n \n\nClick on Carolina Talent r
 egistration link and select the “Request” button to automatically enroll.
DTEND:20260320T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025640Z
DTSTART:20260320T160000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:10 Strategies for Improving Your Finances
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51269586727729
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/10-strategies-for-improving-your-finance
 s-6058
