BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Exhibits
DESCRIPTION:Next in “Rounding Home\,” its eighteenth season\, the Process S
 eries is excited to present Murmuration\, an outdoor soundscape installatio
 n by Jonathon Kirk and Lee Weisert.\n\n \n\nThe performance features one hu
 ndred wirelessly-controlled robotic woodblocks spread throughout the trees 
 of Coker Arboretum\, creating a soundscape that blurs the lines between the
  sounds of nature and music. The project was originally commissioned by the
  North Carolina Arts Council\, receiving additional funding from New Music 
 USA\, and has recently been presented at the South Carolina Botanical Garde
 n in Clemson and the State Arboretum of Virginia in Boyce\, VA.\n\n \n\nAcc
 ording to Weisert\, “The piece explores the possibilities of physical scale
  and complexity in an artistic listening experience.” A wide variety of tex
 tures\, waves\, and gestures reminiscent of the natural sound sources they 
 blend with—from chirping birds in the treetops to the crunching leaves bene
 ath your feet—are generated in real time using tree-mounted woodblocks and 
 computer programming. Describing the process behind the project\, Weisert o
 ffers\, “We are curious to discover to what extent music composition can ‘d
 isappear’ into its surroundings. What role do proximity and distance play i
 n our musical perception and interpretation? How closely can musical form a
 nd natural phenomena coexist?”\n\n \n\nHe adds\, “The piece will hopefully 
 act as a kind of sonic prism for rediscovering Coker Arboretum\,” originall
 y established in 1903\, “which can be easily forgotten within the frenetic 
 activity of campus life.”\n\n \n\nQuestions? Contact us at uncprocessseries
 @gmail.com or visit https://www.processseries.unc.edu/current-season/murmur
 ation
DTEND:20260322T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025640Z
DTSTART:20260322T160000Z
GEO:35.913457;-79.048615
LOCATION:Coker Arboretum
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Murmuration: A Soundscape Installation
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52277734082344
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/murmuration-a-soundscape-installation
END:VEVENT
