CATEGORIES:
DESCRIPTION:Your future starts here! Talk with admissions reps\, get inside
 r tips\, and plan your next move at our Health Professions & Schools Inform
 ation Fair 2026! Registration is recommended but NOT required.\n\n \n\nEven
 t Details:\n\nWhen: Tuesday\, March 24th\, 2026\n\nWhere: The Carolina Club
 \, George Watts Hill Alumni Center \n\nTime: 12-3PM EST\n\n \n\nHow to Prep
 are:\n\nItch to Pitch: Convey who you are\, what experiences you have\, and
  what you're seeking in 30-60 seconds! Check out our website to find our El
 evator Pitch Guide: https://careers.unc.edu/resource/how-to-craft-an-elevat
 or-pitch/. \n\nDress to Impress: Wear professional attire to show you’re se
 rious and prepared! \n\nShow What You Know: Research the employers that are
  attending on Handshake so you can see what roles they are hiring for\, ask
  relevant questions\, and stand out. \n\nHand Away Your Resume: Print multi
 ple copies of your resume so employers/schools can quite literally have it 
 on file.
