BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Exhibits,Ceremony
DESCRIPTION:Join us to celebrate the inaugural cohort of Library AI Fellows
 ! The Library AI Fellows program pairs undergraduate students with the reso
 urces\, mentorship\, and support of the UNC University Library to explore a
 rtificial intelligence in the context of ethics and sustainability. Our fel
 lows have spent the past academic year developing original projects that re
 flect their curiosity\, intellect\, and dedication.\n \nThis showcase event
  features:\n\nProject presentationsQ&A with the fellowsInformation session 
 for students interested in applying to the future cohort of the Library AI 
 Fellows program \n\nAll are welcome! Light snacks will be provided. \n\n \n
 \nThis event is offered by the University Libraries.\n\n \n\nThis event is 
