BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Lectures
DESCRIPTION:UNC-Chapel Hill generates over $1 billion in research annually 
 with discoveries that shape medicine\, technology\, and public health acros
 s North Carolina and beyond. However\, the federal landscape that funds thi
 s work is shifting fast. Join UNC’s Vice Chancellor for Research\, Dr. Penn
 y Gordon-Larsen\, for an inside look at what Carolina scientists are buildi
 ng\, what’s at stake in Washington\, and why it matters to all of us.\n\n \
 n\n🎟️ Free and open to adults\n\n🍴 Light appetizers available for attendees
 \n\n🍻 Drinks available for purchase\n\n \n\n📍Hosted by Morehead Planetarium
  and Science Center at Haw River Tap & Table in Carrboro.
DTEND:20260407T230000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025641Z
DTSTART:20260407T220000Z
GEO:35.910154;-79.068833
LOCATION:Haw River Tap & Table
