X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Meetings and Conferences
DESCRIPTION:Are you ready for the financial decisions that come next?\n\n \
 n\nJoin us for the 3rd Annual Financial Literacy Symposium: Impact – A Path
  You Choose\, designed specifically to help you navigate the real-world mon
 ey choices that often follow your time in school.\n\n \n\nExplore sessions 
 on recent changes to student loan borrowing and repayment\, investing and p
 lanned giving\, managing money in relationships\, navigating NIL and person
 al branding and more. This year is all focused on helping you move forward 
 with clarity and confidence. This experience goes beyond financial literacy
  basics to help you apply what you already know to decisions about earning\
 , spending\, saving\, protecting\, and investing as you step into what’s ne
 xt.\n\n \n\nSaturday\, April 11 | 2:00 – 6:00 pm\nFriday Conference Center\
 n100 Friday Center Drive\, Chapel Hill\, NC\n\n \n\nThis event is free for 
 all UNC Students. In-person attendees will be able to participate in all se
 ssions\, sponsor breaks with activities and receive free food throughout th
 e conference\n\n \n\nIf you’re in\, or near\, Chapel Hill\, you can easily 
 reach the Friday Center via the free N Chapel Hill Transit Saturday route\,
  which stops near the Friday Center Park & Ride Lot\, just a short walk to 
 the conference center. Register here to attend in person: https://mycarolin
 a.unc.edu/register/2026_cfwc_symposium\n\n \n\nIf you’re a UNC Online gradu
 ate or professional student\, a live stream option will be available so you
  can participate too.\n\n \n\nUndergraduate students who attend the entire 
 event in person are eligible to receive CLE credit. \n\nMake time now to in
 vest in your future. We hope you’ll join us.
DTEND:20260411T220000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025641Z
DTSTART:20260411T180000Z
GEO:35.899895;-79.012764
LOCATION:Friday Conference Center
SEQUENCE:0
