BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Stress is experienced in the body as tension. To manage stress 
 we have several choices: reduce or eliminate the stressor\, think about the
  stressor differently so it no longer causes tension or change the way our 
 body reacts to stress. The course will address the third option through exp
 loring a variety of relaxation techniques to calm the body and mind. The cl
 ass will allow participants to learn and experience several simple relaxati
 on tools such as progressive muscle relaxation\, abdominal relaxation breat
 hing.\n\n \n\nWorkshop Objectives\nAt the end of this workshop\, you will b
 e able to:\nIdentify the benefits of relaxation\n• Lowering blood pressure\
 n• Reducing muscle tension and chronic pain\n• Reducing anger and frustrati
 on\n• Improving concentration and creativity\nRecognize the steps to perfor
 m several different relaxation methods such as:\n• Cultivating tension awar
 eness\n• Progressive muscle relaxation\n• Abdominal or diaphragmatic breath
 ing\n• Using sound and voice to relax\n• Laughter\n• Visualization\n\n \n\n
 Click on Carolina Talent registration link and select the “Request” button 
 to automatically enroll.
DTEND:20260513T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025642Z
DTSTART:20260513T160000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Learning to Relax
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51375478845800
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/learning-to-relax-3754
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Immerse yourself in the cosmos with breathtaking views and a mi
 ndful yoga session! Guided by instructor Laura Terry\, this relaxing experi
 ence will be offered in four separate spring sessions in the fulldome theat
 er at Morehead Planetarium.\n\n \n\nYoga Under the Stars is open to older t
 eens and adults of all experience levels. Each session will go from 6-7 pm 
 and costs $30 per person or $25 for Morehead members.\n\n \n\n🎟️ Tickets wi
 ll be available for purchase beginning on Wednesday\, March 11.
DTEND:20260513T230000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025642Z
DTSTART:20260513T220000Z
GEO:35.913753;-79.050409
LOCATION:Morehead Planetarium and Science Center
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Yoga Under the Stars
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_52302893283880
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/yoga-under-the-stars-1708
END:VEVENT
