BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever wondered why your relationship has changed from f
 eeling perfect to full of criticism and devaluation? Do you feel like you a
 re walking on eggshells? This training will demystify narcissism and discus
 s its deep impact on relationships. Additionally\, this session will help y
 ou understand the stages of narcissism\, common manipulation maneuvers and 
 solutions for responding and healing. Key skills addressed will be setting 
 boundaries\, staying calm\, and managing the conversation.\n\nWorkshop Obje
 ctives:\n\n• Define narcissism\n• Recognize the two faces of narcissistic b
 ehavior\n• Understand the relationship cycle\n• Identify common manipulatio
 n tactics\n• Navigate the path to healing and empowerment\n\nClick on Carol
 ina Talent registration link and select the “Request” button to automatical
 ly enroll.
DTEND:20260520T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025642Z
DTSTART:20260520T160000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Responding to Narcissism
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51561087537193
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/responding-to-narcissism
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Immerse yourself in the cosmos with breathtaking views and a mi
 ndful yoga session! Guided by instructor Laura Terry\, this relaxing experi
 ence will be offered in four separate spring sessions in the fulldome theat
 er at Morehead Planetarium.\n\n \n\nYoga Under the Stars is open to older t
 eens and adults of all experience levels. Each session will go from 6-7 pm 
 and costs $30 per person or $25 for Morehead members.\n\n \n\n🎟️ Tickets wi
 ll be available for purchase beginning on Wednesday\, March 11.
DTEND:20260520T230000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025642Z
DTSTART:20260520T220000Z
