BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Stress can compromise healthy breathing habits\, but practicing
  breath work can reduce anxiety\, encourage sleep\, and in some cases\, low
 er blood pressure. Participants will experience a variety of quick\, easy b
 reathing techniques during this course\, and share back their results.\n\n 
 \n\nWorkshop Objectives\nParticipants in this training will:\n• Try a 60-Se
 cond Breathing Meditation\n• Practice Box Breathing\n• Experience 4-7-8 Bre
 athing\n• Review some other Intentional Breathing techniques\n\n \n\nClick 
 on Carolina Talent registration link and select the “Request” button to aut
 omatically enroll.
DTEND:20260527T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025642Z
DTSTART:20260527T160000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Breathing Techniques to Relieve Stress and Improve Health
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51375530213646
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/breathing-techniques-to-relieve-stress-a
 nd-improve-health-6116
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Financial goals are the specific long- and short-term objective
 s to be attained through financial planning and management efforts. Among p
 ersonal financial goals are things such as 1) financial security 2) travel 
 3) education planning 4) retirement planning and 5) estate planning. Being 
 able to succeed in reaching these goals requires a structure and plan with 
 appropriate milestones\, along with the ability to make adjustments along t
 he way.\n\n \n\nWorkshop Objectives\nAt the end of this workshop\, you will
  be able to:\n• Understand the importance of having realistic financial goa
 ls clearly defined\n• Recognize the importance of managing your finances to
  address these goals\n• Develop achievable steps to stay on track\n• Take a
 ppropriate action to monitor progress toward the goals and make adjustments
  as needed.\n\n \n\nClick on Carolina Talent registration link and select t
 he “Request” button to automatically enroll.
DTEND:20260529T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025642Z
DTSTART:20260529T160000Z
LOCATION:
SEQUENCE:0
SUMMARY:Financial Planning for Life
UID:tag:localist.com\,2008:EventInstance_51375548073882
URL:https://calendar.unc.edu/event/financial-planning-for-life
END:VEVENT
