BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:UNC Chapel Hill
CATEGORIES:Workshops and Classes
DESCRIPTION:Organizations are investing in benefits to improve employee wel
 lbeing\, and taking on initiatives to foster a culture of wellbeing in the 
 workplace. However\, many employees still feel that their job is an obstacl
 e to their wellbeing rather than a help. What can you do as a manager to sh
 ift that perception? This session will discuss practical ways to show emplo
 yees that you and your organization support their wellbeing.\n\n \n\nWorksh
 op Objectives\nThis training will help you:\n• Describe ways in which a man
 ager can promote employee wellbeing\n• Become an advocate for wellbeing res
 ources available to your employees\n• Have productive conversations with em
 ployees to address concerns that work is negatively impacting their wellbei
 ng\n• Lead by example in demonstrating that you place a high priority on yo
 ur own wellbeing\n\n \n\nClick on Carolina Talent registration link and sel
 ect the “Request” button to automatically enroll.
DTEND:20260624T170000Z
DTSTAMP:20260409T025642Z
DTSTART:20260624T160000Z
LOCATION:
